extendedInfo.description: Best Android Highway Speed Surfers free games! Games with photos of high speed cars on the highway! Driving at high speed or "road surfing" on the highway is exciting! You enjoy the luxury of sitting in your own car instead of squeezing with many other people in the subway trains. Choose from 3 types of games - puzzle games, memory game and block game. The games are easy to play, fun & addictive!PUZZLE GAMEComplete all the puzzles! Drag the different puzzle pieces to the right place to recreate the highway speed surfers image. More levels of puzzles to be added each month.MEMORY GAMETest your memory in this simple game with the different photos of cars.BLOCK GAMEEnjoy the all time favourite block game. Clear as many rows of blocks as possible to get the highest score! There are 100 levels to be played!What's more! Highway Speed Surfers Free Games app includes a compilation of the funniest highway videos, horrifying highway crash videos, Subway Surfers game cheats videos and Need for Speed game cheats videos.Download Highway Speed Surfers Free Games and have loads of fun!
